{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-member-js","path":"/team/nikil/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ad7708a5-156f-52b3-b988-a4026a7b542f","html":"<p>\"Nikil has over 5 Years of experience in IT infrastructure and digital transformation across mission-driven and public-interest organisations, with a background spanning both technical systems and social design. His work focuses on building stable, scalable, and well-governed technology systems, with particular interest in digital public infrastructure and data-driven approaches to social impact. He is known for translating complex technical systems into practical, sustainable solutions that enable non-technical teams and institutions.</p>\n<p>Outside of work, he enjoys travelling in the mountains, off-roading, and spending time wrenching on his bike.\"</p>","frontmatter":{"name":"Nikil Augustine","role":"Project Manager","description":null,"quote":null,"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":0.6329113924050633,"src":"/static/436b1e1a3bce722d76c971ed494b4f0f/a84be/nikil.jpg","srcSet":"/static/436b1e1a3bce722d76c971ed494b4f0f/fd013/nikil.jpg 200w,\n/static/436b1e1a3bce722d76c971ed494b4f0f/25252/nikil.jpg 400w,\n/static/436b1e1a3bce722d76c971ed494b4f0f/a84be/nikil.jpg 760w","sizes":"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px"}}},"medium":null,"github":null,"linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/nikilaugustine/","twitter":null,"behance":null,"accentcolor":null,"text":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"ad7708a5-156f-52b3-b988-a4026a7b542f"}},"staticQueryHashes":["203280391","2269431855","2668793990"]}